# Site-to-Site IPsec VPN Lab

## Objective
To configure a secure VPN tunnel between two internal networks and validate encrypted communication.

## Tools Used
- GNS3
- Palo Alto / Fortinet Firewall

## Steps Performed
1. Configured IKE Phase 1 (authentication, encryption)
2. Configured IKE Phase 2 (IPsec policies)
3. Created tunnel interfaces
4. Applied security policies to allow traffic
5. Tested connectivity between hosts

## Results
- Successfully established VPN tunnel
- Verified communication between networks
- Identified and resolved policy mismatch issues

## Key Skills Gained
- VPN configuration
- Troubleshooting connectivity issues
- Understanding secure network communication
